Name: TypeOfVideoClip
Description: The type of video clip provided. Supports the use of a controlled vocabulary.

Name: VideoClipBegin
Description: The point to begin the video clip. If no point is provided the assumption is that the start point is the beginning of the clip provided.

Name: VideoClipEnd
Description: The point to end the video clip. If no point is provided the assumption is that the end point is the end of the clip provided.
